jack (0.1.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Plugin-based architecture with hashicorp go-plugin
  * Core plugins: nftables, dnsmasq, wireguard, monitoring
  * Multi-capability plugin support
  * Firewall management with zones, NAT, and port forwarding
  * DHCP and DNS server configuration
  * WireGuard VPN server and client support
  * Static route management with metric-based priority
  * Network interface configuration (bridges, VLANs)
  * System monitoring and health checks
  * Plugin management CLI
  * Unix socket daemon with CLI interface
  * Configuration templates in /etc/jack/templates/

 -- Mono Team <team@mono.si>  Wed, 12 Nov 2025 00:00:00 +0000
